The '''Canecão Mineiro nightclub fire''' occurred on 24 November 2001 in [[Belo Horizonte]], [[Minas Gerais]], [[Brazil]], killing 7 people and injuring 197 others. The fire was caused by [[pyrotechnics]] set off on the stage.
